songs.Title: Father I Adore You
songs.Lyrics: Father I Adore you, I lay my life before You. I will will, love You

songs.Title: Forever You Will Be
songs.Lyrics: Forever You will be, the Lamb upon the throne, I gladly bow my knees, as I worship you Lord

songs.Title: Fragrance To Worship
songs.Lyrics: First it was fragrance, then it turned to, my worship is my weapon, this is how I win my battle

songs.Title: I Have A God
songs.Lyrics: I have a God who never fails, I have a God who never fails, who never fails, forever more

songs.Title: Halleluia
songs.Lyrics: Halle Hale, Oh Halla, Halle Halle, Halleluia

songs.Title: I have more than a song
songs.Lyrics: I have more than a song, today, I brought myself, I am your sacrifice. I am more than a song, today, I brought myself, I am your worship

songs.Title: Adonai we worship you
songs.Lyrics: Adonai we worship you, Son of God You are so good. Almighty God, Halloweth be your name, Your dominion is forever more

songs.Title: Amen Amen
songs.Lyrics: Amen Amen, Blessings and Glory, Wisdom Thanksgiving and Honor, Power and Might belongs to our God, Forever and ever Amen

songs.Title: Anointing fall on me
songs.Lyrics: Anointing fall on me. Anointing fall on me. Let the power of the Holy Ghost fall on me, Anointing fall on me

songs.Title: Be Glorified
songs.Lyrics: Be Glorified, Be Glorified. Be Glorified in the Heavesn. Be Glorified on this earth. Be Glorified in this temple. Jesus, Jesus, be Thou Glorified

songs.Title: Consuming Fire
songs.Lyrics: Consuming fire, I worship You today. You are the all consuming fire, come and manifest yourself

songs.Title: We Bow Down and Worship
songs.Lyrics: We bow down and worship Yahweh. We bow down and worship Yahweh. Yahweh, Yahweh, Yahweh

songs.Title: El Elyon
songs.Lyrics: El Elyon, God Most High. You are Jesus Christ, You are El Elohe Israel

songs.Title: Fill me Up
songs.Lyrics: YOu provide the fire. I provide the sacrifice. You provide the Spirit. I will open up inside. Fill me up God. Fill me up God. Fill me up God. Fill me up

songs.Title: Fire Burning in My Soul
songs.Lyrics: Fire burning in my soul. Pentecostal fire ay. Holy Ghost fire ay. Fire Fire Fire.

songs.Title: Kadosh
songs.Lyrics:
You reign, you ancient Zion's king.
Kadosh, You are mighty on your throne
